        <field description="yes" name="Description">
          <text>An arrow that is coated with cloth soaked in pitch, tar, kerosene, or some similar flammable material. It is set alight before firing. These arrows are commonly used for sending signals, and for setting enemy structures on fire<mdash/>however, they are also effective for setting enemy soldiers on fire.</text>
